column5: Summers here! Well, things have definately changed. Was out at upper Chukuni two nights ago and 1 walleye... ouch, they were in there but no bites... Last night I tried the Keg area and it was a feeding frenzy.. The last two weeks were hit and miss...Where you think they are, they're not, and where you think they're not, they are...All in all it's been great fishing... Dark Green has been slamming.... Mista W
